How can I use HTML and CSS to create a responsive landing page for a new product launch? The landing page should have a sleek and modern design, with a focus on the product's features and benefits. Can you provide some code to help me get started?
[HTML page]
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<title>Product Launch</title>
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
	<header>
		<h1>New Product Launch</h1>
		<nav>
			<ul>
				<li><a href="#features">Features</a></li>
				<li><a href="#benefits">Benefits</a></li>
				<li><a href="#testimonials">Testimonials</a></li>
				<li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
			</ul>
		</nav>
	</header>
	<section id="hero">
		<h2>The Best Product Yet</h2>
		<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed at justo auctor, ultrices felis ac, euismod massa. Praesent malesuada tincidunt ex, eu aliquet ipsum dapibus at. Morbi nec libero purus. Duis malesuada justo sed mauris blandit, sit amet rhoncus nisl vestibulum. Suspendisse potenti.</p>
		<a href="#contact" class="button">Get in Touch</a>
	</section>
	<section id="features">
		<h2>Features</h2>
		<ul>
			<li><i class="fa fa-check"></i>Feature 1</li>
			<li><i class="fa fa-check"></i>Feature 2</li>
			<li><i class="fa fa-check"></i>Feature 3</li>
			<li><i class="fa fa-check"></i>Feature 4</li>
		</ul>
	</section>
	<section id="benefits">
		<h2>Benefits</h2>
		<ul>
			<li><i class="fa fa-check"></i>Benefit 1</li>
			<li><i class="fa fa-check"></i>Benefit 2</li>
			<li><i class="fa fa-check"></i>Benefit 3</li>
			<li><i class="fa fa-check"></i>Benefit 4</li>
		</ul>
	</section>
	<section id="testimonials">
		<h2>Testimonials</h2>
		<blockquote>
			<p>"Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed at justo auctor, ultrices felis ac, euismod massa. Praesent malesuada tincidunt ex, eu aliquet ipsum dapibus at."</p>
			<cite>John Doe</cite>
		</blockquote>
		<blockquote>
			<p>"Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed at justo auctor, ultrices felis ac, euismod massa. Praesent malesuada tincidunt ex, eu aliquet ipsum dapibus at."</p>
			<cite>Jane Smith</cite>
		</blockquote>
	</section>
	<section id="contact">
		<h2>Contact Us</h2>
		<form>
			<input type="text" placeholder="Name">
			<input type="email" placeholder="Email">
			<textarea placeholder="Message"></textarea>
			<button>Send</button>
		</form>
	</section>
</body>
</html>
[HTML page code]
/* Reset */
html, body, ul, li, h1, h2, h3, p, blockquote, form, fieldset, input, textarea, button {
	margin: 0;
	padding: 0;
}
/* Typography */
body {
	font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
	font-size: 16px;
	line-height: 1.5;
	color: #333;
}
h1, h2, h3 {
	font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
	font-weight: 700;
	margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
h1 {
	font-size: 2rem;
}
h2 {
	font-size: 1.5rem;
}
h3 {
	font-size: 1.25rem;
}
p {
	margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}
/* Header */
header {
	background-color: #f8f8f8;
	padding: 1rem;
	position: fixed;
	top: 0;
	left: 0;
	right: 0;
	z-index: 999;
	display: flex;
	align-items: center;
	justify-content: space-between;
}
nav ul {
	list-style: none;
	display: flex;
}
nav li {
	margin-left: 1rem;
}
nav a {
	color: #333;
	text-decoration: none;
}
/* Hero */
#hero {
	background-image: url('https://source.unsplash.com/collection/1080x1080/?product');
	background-size: cover;
	background-position: center;
	height: 80vh;
	display: flex;
	flex-direction: column;
	align-items: center;
	justify-content: center;
	text-align: center;
	color: #fff;
}
#hero h2 {
	font-size: 3rem;
	margin-bottom: 2rem;
}
.button {
	display: inline-block;
	background-color: #333;
	color: #fff;
	padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
	border-radius: 5px;
	margin-top: 2rem;
	font-size: 1.25rem;
	transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
}
.button:hover {
	background-color: #666;
}
/* Sections */
section {
	padding: 4rem 1rem;
}
#features li, #benefits li {
	list-style: none;
	display: flex;
	align-items: center;
	margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}
#features li i, #benefits li i {
	margin-right: 1rem;
	color: #333;
	font-size: 2rem;
}
#testimonials {
	background-color: #f8f8f8;
}
blockquote {
	border-left: 5px solid #333;
	padding-left: 1rem;
	margin-bottom: 2rem;
}
blockquote p {
	font-style: italic;
	margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
cite {
	font-weight: bold;
}
/* Contact Form */
form {
	display: flex;
	flex-direction: column;
	align-items: center;
}
input, textarea {
	padding: 0.75rem;
	margin-bottom: 1rem;
	border-radius: 5px;
	border: 1px solid #ccc;
	width: 100%;
}
textarea {
	height: 150px;
	resize: none;
}
button {
	background-color: #333;
	color: #fff;
	padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
	border-radius: 5px;
	font-size: 1.25rem;
	margin-top: 1rem;
	transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
}
button:hover {
	background-color: #666;
}

Creating a responsive landing page involves using HTML and CSS to ensure that the content looks good on all devices. The code you've provided is a great starting point. Let me help you refine it further by adding some responsive design techniques and a few improvements to ensure a modern and sleek design. 

Here’s a refined version of your code:

### HTML

